# Lessons Learned

## Project Summary

This project provided practical experience in building and operating a cloud-based Security Operations Center (SOC) using Microsoft Sentinel and Azure services. It strengthened my understanding of SIEM technologies, Windows Security Events, Kusto Query Language (KQL), and incident investigation workflows.

---

# Technical Skills Gained

## Microsoft Sentinel

- Created and managed Analytics Rules.
- Investigated Windows Security Events.
- Performed Threat Hunting using KQL.
- Monitored endpoint activity.

---

