# Key Takeaways

- Microsoft Sentinel provides centralized security monitoring.
- Windows Event Logs are essential for threat detection.
- KQL is a powerful language for threat hunting.
- Analytics Rules automate detection of suspicious activities.
- Documentation is as important as technical implementation.
- Mapping detections to MITRE ATT&CK improves investigation quality.

